# Desktop Menu Specification

This document defines how to construct a user-visible hierarchy of applications, typically displayed as a menu. It allows third-party software to add menu items that work for all desktops, and allows system administrators to edit menus in a way that affects all desktops. 


### Mailing list

Discussion of this specification should occur on [[xdg|https://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/xdg]]. 


### Git

The specification is maintained [[in the xdg-specs git repository|https://cgit.freedesktop.org/xdg/xdg-specs/tree/menu]]. See [[Getting Involved|GettingInvolved]] for more on how to contribute.

